This paper discusses the use of machine learning models and techniques to mitigate unwanted biases in data. The paper specifically focuses on the use of adversarial learning to achieve this goal. Given this focus, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
